00:11:15.520 --> 00:11:20.960
the only ones that show up in this table. And then the other thing you can do here is there's

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:28.080
an option called field display names, which lets you change the names that are being shown in those

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:34.880
columns. So I might change title to project. This is sort of more of a project portfolio.

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:40.000
And instead of saying categories, if I'm really using this to kind of show people what I can do,

